      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Notes\n\n- This is not a consumer graph.\n- It exists to be referenced by a **consumer bridge** so the Legend tab can list node classes.\n- Each bridge node should set `target.kind = node-class` and `target.key` for a stable type key."
      }
